OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FJapan to ban upskirting in 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fstronger sex crime laws    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Lawmakers are introducing Japan's first
OL,6, laws against taking sexually           
OL,7, exploitative photos or videos of others
OL,8, without consent.                       
OL,10,FThe bill against "photo voyeurism"     
OL,11,Fwould prohibit acts such as upskirting 
OL,12,Fand secret filming of sexual acts.     
OL,14,FUntil now, such criminal cases had to  
OL,15,Fbe prosecuted under local prefecture   
OL,16,Flaws, which greatly vary in scope.     
OL,18,FThe bill is part of a wider overhaul of
OL,19,FJapan's laws on sex crimes, which will 
OL,20,Falso expand the definition of rape.    
